 E-mail confirmation for registrations&nbsp;(Double opt-in) can be enabled for the website&nbsp;using the <strong><span id="m_c_s_lblDispName22" onmouseout="UnTip()" onmouseover="Tip(''Indicates whether the registration requires confirmation through a link sent by e-mail.'')" style="cursor: help">Registration requires e-mail confirmation</span> </strong>setting, which can be found in&nbsp;<strong>Site Manager -&gt; Settings -&gt; Security &amp; Membership</strong>. For additional information about this functionality, please see <a href="http://devnet.kentico.com/docs/devguide/registration_approval_and_double_opt_in.htm" target="_blank">Registration approval and double opt-in</a> in the Kentico CMS Developer&#39;s Guide.</p>', '7d659195-7568-4516-90d9-57944c2bb65c', '20120425 17:41:31', 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '84895f58-7362-4211-bd97-f33fd81a2689')
